Package org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.statistics.writer

Contains classes to compute various graph statistics and write it in csv data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistinctEdgePropertiesByLabelPreparer
    Computes DistinctEdgePropertiesByLabel for a given logical graph.
    DistinctSourceVertexCountPreparer
    Computes DistinctSourceIds for a given logical graph.
    DistinctTargetVertexCountPreparer
    Computes DistinctTargetIds for a given logical graph and write it in a CSV file.
    DistinctVertexPropertiesByLabelPreparer
    Computes DistinctVertexPropertiesByLabel for a given logical graph and write it in a CSV file.
    EdgeCountPreparer
    Computes EdgeCount for a given logical graph and write it in a CSV file.
    SourceAndEdgeLabelDistributionPreparer
    Computes SourceLabelAndEdgeLabelDistribution for a given logical graph and write it in a CSV file.
    StatisticWriter
    Class to write the statistic of a graph in a file.
    TargetAndEdgeLabelDistributionPreparer
    Computes TargetLabelAndEdgeLabelDistribution for a given logical graph and write it in a CSV file.
    VertexCountPreparer
    Computes VertexCount for a given logical graph and write it in a CSV file.
